<h4><a href="https://hot.cnbeta.com/articles/game/1025321.htm">日本首相候选人在《动森》宣传拉票</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363685" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_5f5496a7bf642.jpg" alt="" width="798" height="447" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_5f5496a7bf642.jpg 798w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_5f5496a7bf642-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_5f5496a7bf642-768x430.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 798px) 100vw, 798px" /></p>
<p>3DMGame 援引日媒消息指，日本首相候选人石破茂在游戏《集合啦！动物森友会》中进行宣传。</p>
<p>策划人表示，这个宣传的出发点在于「不曾接触政治的玩家可以（通过游戏）直接和候选人对话，希望能让他们对政治产生部分兴趣。」美国总统候选人的拜登也曾用《动森》进行宣传。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/9/cactus-plant-flea-market-nike-air-force-1-white-dd7050-100-release-date">耐克 Air Force 1 新联名款公布</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363686" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-7.jpg" alt="" width="1100" height="721" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-7.jpg 1100w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-7-360x236.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-7-768x503.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1-7-1024x671.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，耐克和潮牌 Cactus Plant Flea Market 合作的 Air Force 1 联名款近日放出产品图，预计于 9 月 10 日正式发售。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363687" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-4.jpg" alt="" width="1100" height="756" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-4.jpg 1100w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-4-360x247.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-4-768x528.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2-4-1024x704.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" /></p>
